<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西全身都是亮晶晶的化学物质。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得洗掉这些化学物质！”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们让我变得又痒又生气！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西想起火车事故现场的消防车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>消防员可以用水管往我身上喷水。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐，哐，哐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇呜！哇呜！”蓝狒狒继续往美罗城方向走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得快点行动！”罗西自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在空中飞的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>化学物质进到了她的眼睛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西差点儿碰到了电线，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又差点儿撞在火车车厢上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，罗西落在史密斯侦探身旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮帮我！”罗西叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些化学物质太可怕了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真的好痒啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么帮你？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉消防员让他们向我喷水！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“知道了！”侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>消防员用水管对着罗西喷水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，所有的化学物质都洗掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西叹了口气。“现在好多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她意识到了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道蓝狒狒为什么那么生气了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>化学物质让它发痒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西举起消防车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要借一下这个。”罗西对消防员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她向蓝狒狒飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，蓝狒狒已经到了市内。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇呜！哇呜！”人们边跑边喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只大狒狒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快逃命啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救救我们，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗！罗西把消防车里的水倒在蓝狒狒身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的化学物质都被洗掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝狒狒不再发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它不再跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它也不再挠痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝狒狒坐下来，闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看起来心情好多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！”罗西叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蓝狒狒不再生气了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是它还是很大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它没办法继续巡游了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它也不能回动物园了。“嗯……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西敲着下巴开始思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个月以后，罗西和她的朋友们在杰克家看电视。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当我发现蓝狒狒没有回到动物园的时候很难过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，现在我一点都不难过了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不难过了。”杰克说，“这样更好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“电影开始了。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>电影名字出现在屏幕上：蓝狒狒拯救地球！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真棒！”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很高兴火箭女孩儿把蓝狒狒送到了好莱坞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，它变成大明星了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿真了不起。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔怀疑地看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西只是笑笑，伸手去拿碗里的爆米花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>